write
args = "replicates=100"

So it should work:

me <- maxent(predictors, occtrain, factors=c("bion", "morfo_roc",
"morfo_bloc", "morfo_sedgruesos", "morfo_sedmuyfin", "morfo_veg",
"morfo_sedfinos"), args = "replicates=100")

